{"tid":265682,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"唉 台灣落大雨","createTime":"2017-05-31T22:41:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-01T13:31:01.000Z","uid":65308,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"19f7dfa36472c41a4a5856cbae91d232f94f97ca","tid":265682,"uid":65308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T22:41:40.000Z","msg":"小弟6月2-6月5 去花蓮<br />\n睇天氣預報<br />\n<br />\n6月2-5都係陣雨或雷雨..<br />\n<br />\n２日、３日滯留鋒面及西南氣流影響，各地有陣雨或雷雨，並有豪雨以上等級降雨發生的機率。<br />\n<br />\n４日、５日滯留鋒面影響，各地有陣雨或雷雨，並有局部大雨或豪雨發生的機率。<br />\n<br />\noverall google 話所有時間 90-99% 有雨<br />\n<br />\n依家諗緊不如cancel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲又係依個時間出發去台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24382e458b2b5a88e2edea88282e8aa090a906b4","tid":265682,"uid":5007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T22:53:30.000Z","msg":"上次去台灣都係 還好上機落機兩岸都叫細雨返<br />\n最後都搞到行商場多 得一晚停雨行到夜市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"568090b3b03ca4124107c51306311b6ea28c9dd2","tid":265682,"uid":65308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T23:05:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上次去台灣都係 還好上機落機兩岸都叫細雨返<br />\n最後都搞到行商場多 得一晚停雨行到夜市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我想像到我都會係咁<br />\n<br />\n因為難得請到AL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而且唔去又退唔到錢(只退到少少hostel錢)"},{"pid":"5c1030f7a28444a8c75aaeec0347f2cfab5eff1e","tid":265682,"uid":76610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T23:15:51.000Z","msg":"今日走 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去8日 得一日落雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0885aa3627a393debe3d9e78357995bcb928fa5c","tid":265682,"uid":65308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T00:35:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今日走 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去8日 得一日落雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你就好..<br />\n<br />\n今晩睇下點...唉"},{"pid":"82a16bb6325871332f1d733adab91f63cfecc5cd","tid":265682,"uid":102132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T00:52:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5ead26f37a97d36d370141bece3f90f0e8cb68ac","tid":265682,"uid":37380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T01:20:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去台北<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce6e24daeddc1265fc1d6e1f09cb203b0fdf1b89","tid":265682,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T01:32:38.000Z","msg":"台灣天氣報告唔信得過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過今年係好多雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef1d450eaacb813c24aeb50be3f7a6d0a4263aee","tid":265682,"uid":65308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T01:51:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去台北<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n台北就快好天"},{"pid":"5efca053f4e7a2624186773bd1dbfb2832f4f3bc","tid":265682,"uid":65308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T01:54:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>台灣天氣報告唔信得過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過今年係好多雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n花蓮真係好大雨<br />\n<br />\n端午連假期間受到大雨影響，蘇花公路112.6公里處九宮里路段發生大規模坍方，自28日晚間7時開始就蘇澳至東澳段封閉，導致雙向交通完全中斷。"},{"pid":"2612c028492602e4333d3b14443fa19a5d9755ee","tid":265682,"uid":42624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T02:18:30.000Z","msg":"都係六月頭去台北<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望唔會落狗屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca073d469316ce63d2655cb300a0656719ce0e32","tid":265682,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T02:22:36.000Z","msg":"蘇花公路開返未？"},{"pid":"c1333a7adc3210dc764fd5dcb6cd3b9328349cc8","tid":265682,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T02:23:31.000Z","msg":"我自駕上清境全程大雨，走果陣先好天，屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"673af331a1ee8d83463bcdc00bf02987ab9b177e","tid":265682,"uid":74150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T02:44:43.000Z","msg":"我聽日飛台北<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 差唔多落足一星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"697711f90cf9a74fd4dd4635d8bc973cd40d2753","tid":265682,"uid":55924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T03:11:06.000Z","msg":"星期六去3日台北 頂 3日都會落雨 最憎落雨"},{"pid":"f501404215894e44c8ac6b3b20b72c76613ec369","tid":265682,"uid":39317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T03:14:50.000Z","msg":"我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不能改變天氣 就改變心態<br />\n落雨條街無咁多人 又唔怕熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"809fbf55f822d6c97412ed0e332b2bed1f9dae7e","tid":265682,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T03:30:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我自駕上清境全程大雨，走果陣先好天，屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n落大雨  自駕既優勢又大左"},{"pid":"7ea8e52960984821f25127f98ccce3a941f15424","tid":265682,"uid":65308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T03:37:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我自駕上清境全程大雨，走果陣先好天，屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n落大雨  自駕既優勢又大左</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有車牌真好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a3cba05a005e88124210f60f706ffaed1b4576e","tid":265682,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T03:40:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我自駕上清境全程大雨，走果陣先好天，屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n落大雨  自駕既優勢又大左</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有車牌真好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兩睇啦，我天黑上，又黑又大雨好危險<br />\n<br />\n點知冇野睇，純粹得個揸字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"487ab23fb1bb44f0efdf4c1240b280122848e89e","tid":265682,"uid":5007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T13:31:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>上次去台灣都係 還好上機落機兩岸都叫細雨返<br />\n最後都搞到行商場多 得一晚停雨行到夜市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我想像到我都會係咁<br />\n<br />\n因為難得請到AL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而且唔去又退唔到錢(只退到少少hostel錢)</blockquote><br />\n我覺得安全起機落機緊要過果到落唔落大雨<br />\n豪雨當去住下酒店"}]}